                    <item>
              <title>Blurring the boundaries [ELESIG Videos about learners and technology]</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3462</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3462</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS--><strong>Blurring the boundaries</strong></p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->How do learners integrate their learning with the rest of their lives?</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Videos</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Video clips from interviews recorded at the ELESIG Summer Symposium, July 2008.</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</p>
<p>Video interviews with Jennie Winter, University of Plymouth</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS--><a href="http://ELESIG.ning.com/video/2007026:Video:8157">http://ELESIG.ning.com/video/2007026:Video:8157</a></p>
