              <title>LexDis Participatory Podcasts</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3359</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3359</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>LexDis Participatory Podcasts</strong></p>
<p>Mike Wald, E.A. Draffan and Russell Newman, University of Southampton</p>
<p>Video &amp; blog posts</p>
<p>This project was funded by an ELESIG Small Grant.</p>
<p>This project aims to support researchers of the learner experience to offer participatory research methodologies to disabled students where the learner voice can be raised to offer successful collaboration to ensure a more equitable teaching and learning environment. A series of interviews will be conducted to capture opinions and expertise about participatory research and shared as podcasts.</p>
