<li>A record of external research visits you have made or placements in other institutions/labs. </li>
<li>A record of invitations from you to researchers coming from outside your university. </li>
<li>A record of active participation in an on-line discussion group connected with your research field. </li>
<li>A record of collaboration in a research project. </li>
<li>A record of collaborative training activities with others from different faculties.</li>
</ul>
