<ul>
<li>Positive reports on your feedback to other students.</li>
<li>Reports on your teaching, including feedback and assessment where available. </li>
<li>A record of external teaching experience, outreach work in schools, mentoring and coaching (e.g. sport or theatre).</li>
<li>Copies of lesson plans, lecture notes, hand-outs, PowerPoint slides developed for your teaching, linked to defined learning objectives set.</li>
</ul>
