<li>'Who cares'?:<br /> 
<ul>
<li>Can you identify who is likely to benefit from your research and how they might benefit? </li>
<li>Can you relate your research to a specific 'everyday' problem that it might address, whether directly or indirectly? </li>
<li>Can you explain your research intelligibly to a 14 year old? </li>
