<ul>
<li>paper or poster presented </li>
<li>PowerPoint slides used </li>
<li>new contacts made with people interested in your work </li>
<li>feedback from an observer in the audience on your performance (e.g. in answering questions) </li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Record of effective participation at Open Day. </li>
</ul>
