<p>By the time students complete a PhD, they should be able to answer &lsquo;Yes&rsquo; to most of these questions.</p>
<ul>
<li>Are you able to manage the basic, every-day organisation of your research without having to be nagged or reminded? </li>
<li>Can you resolve minor problems on your own? </li>
<li>Can you make autonomous decisions about the design and conduct of your research? </li>
