<li>A record of use of support, e.g., consultation with experts, counselling. coaching, working with a mentor. </li>
<li>A personal list of sources of support. </li>
<li>A record of active participation in relevant training courses. </li>
<li>A record of your negotiated agreement with your supervisor about something (such as a paper or conference presentation) you are working on together. </li>
</ul>
