<li>Examples      of the databases or spreadsheets used in research.</li>
<li>Construction      and maintenance of a personal website.</li>
<li>Record      of participation in a First Class conference or other web-based      discussions.</li>
<li>Poster.</li>
<li>Slides      prepared for a research seminar.</li>
</ul>
