<div>
<h1>Check this skill</h1>
<p>By the time students complete a PhD, they should be able to answer &lsquo;Yes&rsquo; to most of these questions.</p>
<ul>
<li>Can you identify issues and gaps in the literature in your domain? </li>
<li>Are you able to define the specialist terminology you use and to explain it in plain language to a non-specialist? </li>
